{# V12H-HF4 Real Products Sandbox (NOT included in homepage)
   This file is a research sandbox for future real-product binding experiments.
   DO NOT include this file in index.twig until a working solution is validated.
   
   Known failure modes (V12H through V12H-HF4):
   1. product-card-component="v12-best-seller-card" requires the JS to be a
      standalone Webpack entry point (like wishlist-card.js), NOT bundled into app.js.
   2. Even with standalone chunking, Salla Twilight's hydration timing may conflict
      with the isolateHomepage() MutationObserver that aggressively hides DOM nodes.
   3. CSS-only overrides of native cards (Option B in HF3) failed because the native
      card structure uses Shadow DOM or deep scoping that resists external CSS.
   
   Future research path:
   - Add 'v12-best-seller-card': asset('js/partials/v12-best-seller-card.js') to webpack.config.js
   - Load the standalone chunk via <script defer src="{{ 'v12-best-seller-card.js'|asset }}">
   - Use product-card-component="v12-best-seller-card" in salla-products-list
   - Test on a NON-homepage page first (e.g., a hidden test page) to avoid isolateHomepage() conflicts
   - Only migrate to homepage after visual confirmation
#}

